        <tr><td>Draft door bolt service or replacement</td><td>$80 to $180</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Hinge spring replacement</td><td>$180 to $280</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Hardware corrosion service (coastal)</td><td>$120 to $260</td></tr>
        <tr><td>BGE warranty claim coordination + install labor</td><td>$120 plus labor (parts on warranty)</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Out-of-warranty fire ring (Large)</td><td>$280 to $440</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Out-of-warranty fire box (Large)</td><td>$340 to $520</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Out-of-warranty dome (Large)</td><td>$520 to $780</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Out-of-warranty 2XL ceramic components</td><td>Quote-based, $400-800 typical</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Warranty (SDAR labor)</td><td>90 days parts and labor on our work</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-number">Why us for BGE</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">What separates our BGE service.</h2>
    <ul class="reasons-list">
      <li><strong>Warranty navigation expertise.</strong> We file BGE lifetime ceramic warranty claims on the customer's behalf and don't charge for parts the manufacturer covers.</li>
      <li><strong>Architectural simplicity recognition.</strong> We won't oversell a service call. If the issue resolves at customer education or at a dealer warranty path, we tell you that.</li>
      <li><strong>Parts on the van.</strong> Felt gaskets for Medium, Large, XL; replacement dome thermometers; common fastener hardware.</li>
      <li><strong>Coastal hardware service.</strong> Manhattan Beach, Marina del Rey, Malibu, Newport Beach: bi-annual lubrication and corrosion service for BGE owners on saltwater exposure.</li>
      <li><strong>BHGS #A49573 plus EPA 608 Universal certified #1346255700410.</strong> Verifiable.</li>
      <li><strong>Same-day across LA, OC, Ventura.</strong> Next-day for Riverside and San Bernardino. 24/7 phone.</li>
      <li><strong>BBB A+ verifiable.</strong> See our <a href="/credentials/licensed/">license credentials</a>.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section-gray">
  <div class="container narrow">
    <p class="section-number">FAQ</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Big Green Egg repair questions.</h2>
    <div class="faq-list">
      {faqs.map(f => (<details class="faq-item"><summary>{f.q}</summary><p>{f.a}</p></details>))}
